snippet.title: Terra Battle: Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Mobile RPG "Terra Battle" by MISTWALKER official Trailer

----
Terra Battle Download Starter has Launched!!
----
"New content will be added from new exciting artists based on the number of downloads."


The Download Starter is a project where the number of downloads for Terra Battle
determines content being unlocked such as artists creating new art, new game modes, and the production of books and action figures.

For more detail: http://www.terra-battle.com/en/downloadstarter/
----

Official Site： http://www.terra-battle.com/en
Official Twitter： https://twitter.com/terra_battle_en
Official Facebook： https://www.facebook.com/terrabattle.en

©MISTWALKER
